  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "CRITICAL: Use React Native primitives ONLY (`View`, `Text`, `Image`, `TouchableOpacity`, `ScrollView`, `FlatList`, `TextInput`, `StyleSheet.create`). Do NOT use HTML/CSS elements (div, span) or Tailwind.",
    "Implement navigation using Expo Router or React Navigation.",
    "The application must exclusively follow the dark theme palette provided (`background_base`: #050505). Ensure text contrast meets APCA/WCAG standards using the white/silver provided.",
    "Use `@expo/vector-icons` (e.g., Ionicons, MaterialCommunityIcons) for icons to match the high-end fitness aesthetic. Keep them sharp and minimalist.",
    "All interactive elements MUST include a `testID` attribute for automated testing. Example: `<TouchableOpacity testID='login-submit-button'>`.",
    "For the WhatsApp Checkout functionality, utilize React Native's `Linking.openURL('whatsapp://send?phone=NUMBER&text=MESSAGE')`.",
    "To emulate the 'Exclusive Club' feel, use ample padding (`24px` to `32px` in layout containers), thin `1px` borders (`#262626`), and maintain pure black backgrounds. Avoid rounded corner extremes (stick to `4px` or `8px` radii, avoid pill shapes except occasionally).",
    "Do NOT use generic placeholders (like via.placeholder.com). Strictly use the images provided in the media section of this JSON.",
    "For typography, if you cannot load custom fonts (Montserrat), fallback to the system default sans-serif font, utilizing `fontWeight: '800'` and `letterSpacing: -1` for large headings."
  ]
}